        <body>
            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="KR5e0001-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_003-2a.441" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-07T19:42:15.916+09:00">Also, at birth, all humans contain heavenly breath, and come out when replete [with it].</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_003-2a.442" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T01:56:53.703+09:00">The head, round</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_003-2a.443" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T01:57:23.601+09:00">is heaven;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_003-2a.444" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T01:57:37.844+09:00">the feet, square</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_003-2a.445" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T01:57:54.146+09:00">are earth;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_003-2a.446" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T01:58:10.607+09:00">the four limbs</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_003-2a.447" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T01:58:23.615+09:00">are the four seasons;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_003-2a.448" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T01:58:40.404+09:00">the five viscera</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_003-2a.449" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T01:58:51.773+09:00">are the five agents;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_003-2a.450" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T01:59:31.074+09:00">the ears, eyes, mouth and nose</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_003-2a.451" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:00:07.553+09:00">are the seven regulators [and/or] the three luminaries.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_003-2a.452" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:00:52.629+09:00">It is impossible to account completely for this;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_003-2a.453" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:02:31.958+09:00">only sage persons (or: the sage) know [about it].</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_003-2a.454" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:02:08.287+09:00">At birth, all humans are replete with Yin and Yang;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_003-2a.455" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:03:48.555+09:00">when [the required number of] days and months are fulfilled, they open up the womb and emerge from the opening;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_003-2a.456" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:05:53.562+09:00">&lt;seeing heaven and earth, they resume growing (?)&gt;.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_003-2a.457" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:05:38.016+09:00">Together they will perpetuate their forefathers' lineage,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_003-2a.458" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:06:22.352+09:00">help heaven bring forth beings [and]</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_003-2a.459" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:07:14.481+09:00">help earth nourish the forms (= physical bodies) [of these beings].</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-11a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:08:12.437+09:00">Inner radiance of the cerulean light,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-11a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:08:32.619+09:00">Grand darkness, numerous breaths,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-11a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:08:45.515+09:00">At the same position as the kidneys,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-11a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-07T19:33:08.912+09:00">The location of Ren (S9) and Gui (S10). [S1–10=十天干]</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-11a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-07T19:33:21.239+09:00">Hai (B12) and Zi (B1) are consubstantial, [B1–12=十二地支]</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-11a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:10:31.303+09:00">They embrace one another within the cycle.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-11a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:11:00.785+09:00">Peaking Yin brings forth Yang;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-11a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:11:22.473+09:00">it is called the initial novena.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-11a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:11:45.431+09:00">Once joined, they conceive beings.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-11a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:12:07.997+09:00">Yin comes to a stop [and] Yang rises.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-11a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:14:42.474+09:00">Impregnation [takes place] in Hai (B12),</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-11a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:14:58.574+09:00">Gestation [takes place] in Ren (S9),</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-11a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:15:24.444+09:00">Proliferation [takes place] in Zi (B1).</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-11a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:15:42.391+09:00">Generation after generation,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-11a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:18:11.562+09:00">Yang enters in the middle of Yin,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-11a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:18:41.981+09:00">Its bringing forth is ceaseless.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-36a.32" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-07T19:36:08.014+09:00">It is like the myriad beings, which end up dying in Hai (B12).</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-36a.33" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:21:00.347+09:00">[Trigram] Qian, since it marks the commencement [of the cycle], establishes [its] position at the gate of heaven.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-36a.34" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:21:20.293+09:00">Solidification of semen begins in Hai (B12),</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-36a.35" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:27:15.122+09:00">gestation [takes place] in Ren (S9) and the form (physical body) takes shape.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-36a.36" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:27:42.078+09:00">[On] the initial novena, in Zi (B1), the sun begins to return,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-36a.37" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:28:06.32+09:00">[On] the second novena, in Chou (B2), Yin and Yang are set in motion.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-36a.38" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:28:30.81+09:00">[On] the third novena in Yin (B3),</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-36a.39" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:29:33.861+09:00">heaven, earth, humans and the myriad beings, all wanting to turn their back on Yin and face Yang, </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-36a.40" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:30:01.619+09:00">peek in Yin (B3).</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-36a.41" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:30:24.272+09:00">Therefore the myriad beings begin to spread roots in the northeast [and]</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-36a.42" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:30:38.183+09:00">and show their head in Yin (B3).</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-36a.43" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:30:55.99+09:00">Among plants, the large ones</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-36a.44" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:32:28.049+09:00">take [agent] Wood as their chief,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-36a.45" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:32:17.501+09:00">therefore Yin (B3) corresponds to Wood beginning its life,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-36a.46" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:32:52.748+09:00">and Jia (S1) best corresponds to the commencement of Wood.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-36a.47" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:33:49.277+09:00">Therefore the myriad beings appear in Jia (S1) and Yin (B3)</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-36a.48" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:33:41.372+09:00">and eventually die in Gui (S10) and Hai (B12).</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-36a.49" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:36:49.707+09:00">Therefore Wood, when receiving the mandate [of life], is born in the middle of [agent] Water, the great Yin [of/and] primordial breath,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-36a.50" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:38:33.423+09:00">and therefore Jia/Zi (S1/B1) marks the commencement.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-87a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:39:26.482+09:00">Heaven is the beginning of numbers.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-87a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:40:22.273+09:00">For this reason, when heaven and earth are not yet separated,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-87a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:40:45.231+09:00">accumulated breaths are all united as one,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-87a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:40:59.466+09:00">[then] divide into two,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-87a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:41:44.111+09:00">[and] constitute husband and wife.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-87a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:42:02.312+09:00">Heaven descends and impregnates earth;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-87a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:44:15.456+09:00">gestation [takes place] in cerulean obscurity (North),</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-87a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:50:19.589+09:00">[whose cyclical] characters are Jia and Zi (S1/B1).</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-87a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:43:24.259+09:00">[Plants] spread roots in the North-East,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-87a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:43:43.808+09:00">[whose characters are] Chou (B2) and Yin (B3);</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-87a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:44:09.311+09:00">they emerge in Mao (B4) (East);</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-87a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:44:42.923+09:00">they complete sprouting in the South-East,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-87a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:45:29.056+09:00">[whose characters are] Chen (B5) and Si (B6);</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-87a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:45:59.506+09:00">[let] branches hang in the South</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-87a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:47:43.616+09:00">and [get] nurtured in Wu (B7);</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-87a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:48:41.672+09:00">they get old in the South-West,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-87a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:48:31.659+09:00">[whose characters are] Wei (B8) and Shen (B9);</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-87a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:49:08.442+09:00">and [reach] completion in the western sector,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-87a.20" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:49:26.316+09:00">[where] the sun sets, in You (B10).</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-87a.21" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:49:50.401+09:00">Storage is completed in the North-West,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-87a.22" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:50:08.835+09:00">[whose characters are] Xu (B11) and Hai (B12).</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:51:49.597+09:00">Eyes closed, looking inwards,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T03:00:16.683+09:00">come into contact with the divine (or: spirits). &lt;punctuation modified&gt; The numinous,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:52:47.225+09:00">not emitting words,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:53:34.482+09:00">are on a par with the Way.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:53:56.347+09:00">Yin and Yang overturning one another is what heaven has established.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T03:00:55.825+09:00">The art of long life can open the eyes.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:55:53.5+09:00">Do not force back feelings, you should be harmonious and magnanimous.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:56:37.422+09:00">Heaven and earth are harmonized as if [they were] blind and deaf.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:57:57.525+09:00">Want to know its meaning—the child in the womb,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:59:26.214+09:00">Not eating [for] ten months and in contact with the divine (or: spirits),</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:58:48.193+09:00">The way of spontaneity is unsurpassed,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.20" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T02:59:58.99+09:00">Unseeing, and yet the dwelling of breath is twelve-fold.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.21" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T03:01:27.125+09:00">Therefore revert to infancy, then there will be nothing ominous,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.22" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T03:02:04.692+09:00">The old will revert to youth and be in contact with the way.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.23" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T03:02:49.24+09:00">For this reason paint an image twelve times.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.24" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T03:03:06.338+09:00">The righteous obtain goodness,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.25" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T03:03:30.309+09:00">the unworthy, only the ominous.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.26" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T03:03:47.634+09:00">The heavenly way is perennial,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.27" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T03:04:01.736+09:00">it cannot cease to be,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.28" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T03:04:31.939+09:00">In the manner of the four seasons, it circles back to [its] native place,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.29" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T03:05:22.021+09:00">Old age reverts to the beginning,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.30" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T03:05:38.841+09:00">thus [attaining] long life.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-6a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T03:06:54.074+09:00">Value solely spontaneity,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-6a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T03:07:41.077+09:00">the form (= physical body) and the divine (or: spirits) keep to each other.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-6a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T03:08:00.025+09:00">These two mutually embrace one another,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-6a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T03:08:27.901+09:00">He who has singular thoughts, on the contrary, is at fault.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-6a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T03:08:51.657+09:00">Loose spontaneity</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-6a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T03:09:05.496+09:00">and you cannot [achieve] longevity.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-6a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T03:09:28.006+09:00">The five essences of the infant</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-6a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-03T03:09:45.526+09:00">return to preserve oneself.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-33a.98" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T00:43:02.535+09:00">Yin is basically empty.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-33a.99" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T00:43:19.139+09:00">Only once Yang has spread and transformed substance in the middle of Yin,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-33a.100" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T00:43:31.385+09:00">which, being menial and despicable, fears Yang,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-33a.101" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T00:44:23.308+09:00">does [Yin] obediently nourish it,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-33a.102" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T00:44:53.238+09:00">not daring to reject [it].</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-33a.117" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T00:45:29.357+09:00">Now the vulgar say</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-33a.118" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T00:45:41.279+09:00">that Yang generates and Yin develops,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-33a.119" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T00:46:12.257+09:00">[yet] Yin only follows, nourishing and developing the Yang substance.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-23a.250" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T00:51:49.172+09:00">Earth</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-23a.251" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T00:52:06.99+09:00">is the lowness of Yin.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-23a.252" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T00:52:18.156+09:00">Water</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-23a.253" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T00:52:37.659+09:00">is the intensity of Yin</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-23a.254" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T00:56:49.83+09:00">[and] belongs to earth.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-23a.255" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T00:53:15.488+09:00">Yin presides over gestation.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-23a.256" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T00:53:46.951+09:00">Generally, when beings are harmed while pregnant,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-23a.257" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T00:54:11.338+09:00">there will be bleeding.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-23a.258" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T00:54:05.688+09:00">Blood</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-23a.259" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T00:54:29.142+09:00">is of the category of water.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-23a.260" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T00:54:40.08+09:00">[Any living being] harmed while pregnant</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-23a.261" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T00:54:49.498+09:00">will be angry and displeased;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-23a.262" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-07T19:57:17.158+09:00">furthermore, by bleeding, it will perpetrate pollution [and] harm [other] people.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-23a.263" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T00:56:58.441+09:00">Watercourses,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-23a.264" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T00:55:53.375+09:00">being the blood vessels of earth,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-23a.265" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T00:55:50.109+09:00">are the Yin of earth.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-23a.266" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T00:56:13.078+09:00">Yin, being menial,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-23a.267" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T00:56:45.539+09:00">when angry must attack and kill people by this personification.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-36a.584" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T01:03:58.934+09:00">It is like the unknowing infant [who],</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-36a.585" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T01:04:12.428+09:00">still in the womb,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-36a.586" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T01:04:21.612+09:00">goes around following its mother’s person.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-36a.587" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T01:04:33.183+09:00">How could it know that the heavenly way is vast, far-reaching, and without confines?</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_003-2a.394" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T01:09:02.416+09:00">Suppose that, in the realm, a single family kills one female;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_003-2a.395" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T01:09:32.118+09:00">how many hundreds of thousands of families [are there] in the realm?</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_003-2a.396" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T01:09:44.611+09:00">Sometimes a dozen females get killed in a single family;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_003-2a.397" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T01:10:18.912+09:00">sometimes pregnant [women] who have not yet given birth</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_003-2a.398" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T01:10:53+09:00">are injured.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_003-2a.399" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T01:11:12.503+09:00">Their breath, stricken by injustice, ascends and moves Heaven.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_003-2a.400" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T01:11:27.39+09:00">How can there be such nonsense?</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_002-24a.71" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T01:13:00.883+09:00">If [one] incessantly practices benevolence</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_002-24a.72" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T01:13:23.72+09:00">and surpasses these [orders of] longevity, it is called "to pass through generations."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_002-24a.73" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T01:13:32.834+09:00">[Those who] incessantly practice malevolence</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_002-24a.74" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T01:13:40.035+09:00">do not reach [these] three [orders of] longevity</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_002-24a.75" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T01:14:03.48+09:00">—they all die prematurely.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_002-24a.76" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T01:14:24.461+09:00">Those who die an embryo in the womb as well as underage persons</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_002-24a.77" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T01:15:14.015+09:00">are called "innocents inheriting the burden of [their] forefathers’ transgressions."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.4100" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T04:00:28.219+09:00">Therefore, their initiation, guidance, and tuition rest with masters;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.4101" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T04:00:44.308+09:00">only then will it be possible to make it that there is nothing [they] do not know.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.4102" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-07T19:41:37.025+09:00">He who does not open up his gate,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.4103" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T04:01:31.997+09:00">even though he receives the authentic way of heaven,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.4104" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T04:01:37.825+09:00">knows not a single thing;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.4105" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T04:01:47.967+09:00">he is like an infant who, at birth,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.4106" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T04:01:59.034+09:00">would be abandoned in a single room</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.4107" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T04:02:07.81+09:00">and not guided to study actively:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.4108" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T04:02:10.793+09:00">there is nothing he might learn.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_009-5a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T04:31:02.385+09:00">For weakness</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_009-5a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T04:31:18.517+09:00">is how the way operates.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_009-5a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T04:31:26.401+09:00">Solitude</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_009-5a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T04:31:38.747+09:00">is a requisite of the way.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_009-5a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-07T19:40:36.325+09:00">Thus the single Northern Pole star,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_009-5a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-07T19:40:38.918+09:00">is followed by the multitude of stars;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_009-5a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T04:32:55.038+09:00">its loneliness contains the multitude.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_009-5a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T04:33:12.232+09:00">The requisite of the way is unity, and yet the way assembles.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_009-5a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T04:33:49.405+09:00">This is the reason why the king of the realm is the paragon of solitude,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_009-5a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T04:34:03.173+09:00">and yet the realm helps [him] rule;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_009-5a.20" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T04:34:25.25+09:00">[this is] the effect of [the multitude] helping the single.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_009-5a.21" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T04:35:29.598+09:00">The father and mother are of utmost strength,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_009-5a.22" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T04:34:51.841+09:00">and yet they help the infant;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_009-5a.23" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-06T04:35:03.135+09:00">this is the effect of the strong helping the weak.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.4089" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-07T19:26:59.531+09:00">Therefore the major sages of antiquity instructed people to deeply meditate and have far-reaching thoughts,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.4090" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-07T19:27:09.979+09:00">to shut their nine [bodily] apertures,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.4091" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-07T19:27:20.337+09:00">to rest their four limbs,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.4092" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-07T19:27:30.784+09:00">to make themselves chaotic,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.4093" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-07T19:27:43.174+09:00">like a circle without end,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_004-1a.4094" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-07T19:28:14.897+09:00">[and] to emulate a child in the womb, without attending affairs.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_005-44a.41" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-07T19:29:42.862+09:00">First to appease [one’s] perceptible form (= physical body).</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_005-44a.42" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-07T19:29:54.739+09:00">Start doing so</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_005-44a.43" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-07T19:30:02.828+09:00">by emulating an infant at play,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_005-44a.44" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-07T19:30:14.606+09:00">[who] does not use physical strength</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_005-44a.45" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-07T19:30:37.255+09:00">[but] uses only good intentions.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_007-68a.102" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-07T19:48:59.58+09:00">Those who lust for riches and sensuality</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_007-68a.103" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-07T19:49:12.407+09:00">disregard the resulting hardships—</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_007-68a.104" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-07T19:49:35.25+09:00">calamities extending to [unborn descendants in] the womb,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_007-68a.105" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-07T19:49:43.714+09:00">[who] will never see the sun, moon and stars.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_007-68a.106" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-07T19:49:45.145+09:00">What a painful grief!</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_007-138a.70" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-07T19:51:32.465+09:00">It is like a child in the womb.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_007-138a.71" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-07T19:51:48.449+09:00">There can be not [even] minor damage,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_007-138a.72" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-07T19:53:24.131+09:00">[otherwise the child would] inevitably be injured and die;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_007-138a.73" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-07T19:52:12.434+09:00">once dead it would not revive,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_007-138a.74" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-07T19:53:33.347+09:00">and inevitably, a person would be lost.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_007-138a.75" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-07T19:53:43.793+09:00">Would such continuous injuring [of unborn children] not cease,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_007-138a.76" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-07T19:53:54.126+09:00">then [an entire lineage] would become extinct and be deprived of later generations.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_007-138a.77" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-07T19:54:14.873+09:00">A family without lineage would be eradicated.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_007-138a.106" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-07T19:59:36.035+09:00">Yin and Yang unite and conceive in the middle.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_007-138a.107" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-07T19:59:45.643+09:00">Therefore, gestation generally</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_007-138a.108" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-07T19:59:56.828+09:00">takes place below the head and above the feet,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_007-138a.109" xml:lang="en" resp="#gresp" modified="2022-10-07T20:00:06.655+09:00">in the central, abdominal [part of the mother’s body].</seg>
                </p>
            </div>
